result.deskripsine:
Dinosaurs Time is an addon whose main objective is to improve your gaming experience while searching for fossils to recreate the dinosaurs.

 From the small compsognathus to the great spinosaurus, the addon has a grand list of all the InGen species already registered, the majority of which have already been adapted for it, and the others that have not yet been added, will soon be available in the game.
yDino is here!With this amazing add-on you can play with 60 dinosaurs in your game!All with amazing animations!

Prehistoric Life is an ADDON created for all people who want to have a new experience in the game as it adds more than 30 large and powerful, passive and aggressive Dinosaurs, Herbivores, Omnivores, Carnivores, Semi-aquatic and Flying,Small, Medium and GiantThe most important thing is that they can all be tamed in some you can put a saddle to go on a trip.

With this add-on you add a variety of new animals that will appear in our Minecraft worlds.

Most animals are aggressive, others can be domesticated to defend against mobs and some animals can be ridden.

yCreatures, an amazing super complete add-on that brings even more fun to your Minecraft worlds!!This addon contains several new animals for your game, some cute, some not so friendly, but all amazing and super fun, with various varieties of animation, behavior, models and textures.
